# Key Notation
<C->         [Key][Movement][Editing][Visual][Window] Control key (Example: <C-w> means Ctrl + w)
<S->         [Key][Movement][Editing][Visual] Shift key
<M->         [Key] Alt key (Meta)
<Space>      [Key][Leader] Space bar
<CR>         [Key] Enter / Return
<Esc>        [Key][Editing][Visual] Escape key
<Tab>        [Key] Tab key

# Movement
h            [Movement] Move left
j            [Movement] Move down
k            [Movement] Move up
l            [Movement] Move right
w            [Movement] Jump by start of words (forward)
b            [Movement] Jump by start of words (backward)
e            [Movement] Jump by end of words (forward)
ge           [Movement] Jump by end of words (backward)
0            [Movement] Start of line
^            [Movement] Start of line (non-blank)
$            [Movement] End of line
gg           [Movement] Go to first line
G            [Movement] Go to last line
<C-u>        [Movement] Up half page
<C-d>        [Movement] Down half page
<C-f>        [Movement] Page down
<C-b>        [Movement] Page up
%            [Movement] Go to matching bracket

# Editing
i            [Editing] Insert before cursor
a            [Editing] Insert after cursor
I            [Editing] Insert at line start
A            [Editing] Insert at line end
o            [Editing] Append new line below
O            [Editing] Append new line above
r            [Editing] Replace one character
R            [Editing] Enter replace mode
x            [Editing] Delete character
dd           [Editing] Delete line
D            [Editing] Delete to end of line
yy           [Editing] Yank (copy) line
y$           [Editing] Yank to end of line
p            [Editing] Paste after cursor
P            [Editing] Paste before cursor
u            [Editing] Undo
<C-r>        [Editing] Redo
.            [Editing] Repeat last command

# Visual Mode
v            [Visual] Visual mode (char)
V            [Visual] Visual mode (line)
<C-v>        [Visual] Visual mode (block)

# Window Management
<C-w>h       [Window] Move to left window
<C-w>j       [Window] Move to window below
<C-w>k       [Window] Move to window above
<C-w>l       [Window] Move to right window
<C-w>s       [Window] Split horizontal
<C-w>v       [Window] Split vertical
<C-w>c       [Window] Close window
<C-w>o       [Window] Close all other windows

# Search & Replace
/pattern     [Search] Search forward
?pattern     [Search] Search backward
n            [Search] Next match
N            [Search] Previous match
:%s/old/new/g [Search] Replace all in file

# Files
:w           [Files] Save file
:q           [Files] Quit
:q!          [Files] Quit without saving
:wq          [Files] Save and quit
:x           [Files] Save and quit

# Leader (Example)
<Space>f     [Leader] Find file (Telescope)
<Space>g     [Leader] Live grep (Telescope)
<Space>e     [Leader] Toggle explorer
